der\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"rt-item-title\" style=\"\">Martin Brian<\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"rt-item-designation\" style=\"\">UI Designer<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"rt-item-content\" style=\"\">The courses here exceeded my expectations in many regards, especially in the depth of information supplied. In a very non-threatening environment, I learned key principles of design that I can implement immediately.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rt-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rt-item-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"92\" height=\"92\" src=\"https:\/\/radiustheme.com\/demo\/wordpress\/eikra\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/user8-92x92.jpg\" class=\"img-circle wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/radiustheme.com\/demo\/wordpress\/eikra\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/user8-92x92.jpg 92w, https:\/\/radiustheme.com\/demo\/wordpress\/eikra\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/user8-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/radiustheme.com\/demo\/wordpress\/eikra\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/user8-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/radiustheme.com\/demo\/wordpress\/eikra\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/user8-200x200.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 92px) 100vw, 92px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rt-item-content-holder\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"rt-item-title\" style=\"\">David Fahim<\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"rt-item-designation\" style=\"\">Web Developer<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"rt-item-content\" style=\"\">Excellent content and assignments that build on your knowledge, reinforce, and then expand. I recently secured new employment using PHP and couldn&#039;t have done so without the Professional Web Development courses.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n<\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row full_width=&#8221;stretch_row&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1510745269573{borde